<para><formalpara>
<title>Description</title>
<para><itemizedlist>
<listitem>
<para>This module implements the Covariance Matrix Adaptation Evolution Strategy (CMA-ES) for optimization tasks. It provides a framework for minimizing scalar functions using evolutionary strategies, with support for parallel execution and adaptive stopping criteria.</para>
</listitem><listitem>
<para>The implementation is based on the original CMA-ES algorithm and has been optimized for performance using NumPy and SciPy libraries.</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
